237
00:13:14,290 --> 00:13:17,510
*I'm coming out,
so get the party started*

238
00:13:17,520 --> 00:13:21,000
*I'm coming out, I'm coming
out, I'm coming out...*

239
00:13:25,580 --> 00:13:27,850
Ehi, buone notizie. Non devi piu'
essere di malumore a causa di Penny.

240
